CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 2, 1957, pg. 13, reads: "TV Panelist - Mrs. Willa Mae Rice will be among the speakers on the 'World Day of Prayer' panel on KDKA TV, March 3, at 11 A. M.  Other representatives of the Allegheny Council of Churchwomen include Mmes. Craig Stockdale, Wallace McCurdy, Edward Moyer, Walter R. Clyde and E. Roy Gorman."
TitMainTitle: Willa Mae Rice and Raymond Rice posed in front of seascape backdrop in Harris Studio, horizontal format
